Class Option<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.base.Option<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the type of the contained object
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Option.Error, Option.None, Option.Some

    public abstract class Option<T>
extends Object
    A class representing a value, an exception or nothing. These classes are used by materialize and dematerialize operators.
    Author:
    akarnokd
